# ReceiptHawk – AI Expense Tracker (In Progress)

A smart expense tracking system that allows users to upload receipts and automatically extract and categorize expense data.

## Features
- Upload receipt images
- OCR-based text extraction (in progress)
- Automatic expense categorization


## Tech Stack
- React
- JavaScript
- OCR (planned)

## Status
🚧 Currently under development

## Future Enhancements
- Analytics dashboard
- Expense insights
- Cloud storage integration
